    "Lastly, Valmeekam et al. (2021) design an approach where users can challenge the plan suggested by a system via alternative plans or \"foils\", and the system crafts an explanation contrasting the plans.",
    "Lastly, the study by Gao et al. (2021) uses a scripted interaction sequence in a controlled setting.",
    "The authors designed a concise dialogue consisting of three questions with binary response options followed by an open question to gather feedback.",
